dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2852,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/10\/hadha-sirat-al-mustaqeem\/","url_meta":{"origin":32481,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Islam: This is the straight path to Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 10, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Mas'ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, drew a line in the sand with his hand and he said, \u201cThis is the straight path of Allah.\u201d Then, the Prophet drew lines to the right and left, saying, \u201cThese are other paths, and there is\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33238,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/18\/forsake-sunnah-not-muhammad\/","url_meta":{"origin":32481,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Sunnah: Whoever forsakes Sunnah is not part of Muhammad","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 18, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever does not desire my Sunnah is not a part of me.\u201d Source: al-Sunnah li-Ibn Abi\u0304 \u2018A\u0304s\u0323im 52 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0645\u0652\u0631\u064d\u0648 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\